rComments: Smart and distinguished in his field but absolutely horrendous at teaching. No idea what I was supposed to learn.

If I could give less than 1 for prof quality I would. I have never had prof who was so poor at explaining concepts. He was also extremely rude to students who asked questions. His slides are hard to follow and honestly don't really clear up the many things he leaves unclear. He's smart, but has not a clue how to teach or respect his students.
teacherRatingTags: ['Graded by few things', 'Test heavy', 'Clear grading criteria']
